query:
SELECT c.kind, c.eth_tx_id
            FROM tee_dcap_collateral c
            WHERE c.eth_tx_id IS NOT NULL
              AND c.update_guard_expires < $1
              AND NOT EXISTS (
                  SELECT 1
                  FROM eth_txs_history h
                  WHERE h.eth_tx_id = c.eth_tx_id
                    AND h.sent_successfully = true
              )
